ncluded before December 12, 2020. “We therefore appeal to our States, Local Governments and Wards leaders to take all the necessary steps to ensure smooth and transparent registration exercise. We will continue to provide update of the process on regular basis”, Gov. Buni stated. Vanguard News Nigeria The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP has distanced itself from the inclinations of former President Olusegun Obasanjo on the continuance of Alhaji Aminu Tambuwal as Speaker of the House of Representatives and membership of the party of former Governor of Ogun State, Otunba Gbenga Daniel. September 9, 2011 In "Headlines" Ahead of the 2019 general elections, the All Progressives Congress APC has embarked on a new membership drive. August 22, 2018 In "News" The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, is to commence the revalidation of all its members across the country next month, raising fears of another round of infighting by power blocs within the party. August 3, 2011 In "News"